<h1>Youngest director</h1>

<p>
  The youngest director in our dataset right now is
  <%= link_to @youngest_director.name, "/directors/#{@youngest_director.id}" %>,
  <% if @youngest_director.dob.present? %>
    born on <%= @youngest_director.dob.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.
  <% else %>
    but their date of birth is unknown.
  <% end %>
</p>

<p>
  (<a href="http://strftime.net/">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)
</p>
